I think about so many things,
so fast that I can't remember what it was.
But when I think about you, 
the thought dosen't just run past at lighting speed.
I keep that thought in my mind,
because you never get off my mind,
you never have.
Sometimes, when I'm alone, I think of you,
only you.
When people ask what I'm thinking about, I say
it's you, 
because you're the first thought that comes to mind.
My mind never rests,even when asleep.
My mind will never rest,
even when dead and rotting.